{"tid":1174631,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港地買樓真係唔難，最緊要識錢搵錢","createTime":"2019-05-28T03:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T11:03:44.000Z","uid":150100,"like":10,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"44d8fcd2e3122ac72e442309da05eb61a8a9d801","tid":1174631,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:50:45.000Z","msg":"假設你每個月返工扣除開支淨袋10000<br />\n攞5000出嚟買主客和8串1，一中就基本上翻幾倍，然後再買，又再翻幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好同我講咩唔中點算，得嗰3個揀都揀唔中就死咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後仲有嗰5000就先儲起佢，唔係叫你儲嚟買樓，因為白痴先會儲錢嚟買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲錢係儲嚟投資中資股<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係人都知貿易戰一定係中國贏㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國一贏，啲股價一定爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁到時你再放返出去<br />\n起碼都入手價翻幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再加埋你喺馬會賺返嚟啲錢<br />\n唔好話御半山<br />\n半山都嚟緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以話<br />\n你班廢青日日喺度抱怨話上車難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上車根本就唔難，月薪15k已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難係因為你地唔識錢搵錢啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bc61d1ffd9aa0ffebf774e044657d2754cfb5f","tid":1174631,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:51:10.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"a37273338773d552476c66124c3d984233c0a837","tid":1174631,"uid":139322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:51:56.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"4bf9a46319c460199cc4eaff0f1c5457fe27d447","tid":1174631,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:53:50.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"953cb1a4492d49bd6e4504c8178984940c606022","tid":1174631,"uid":150